name: Frog On Top Studios
tag_list: web, development, full-service, design, ecommerce, flash, multimedia, blog
overview:
Frog On Top Studios has been providing high-quality web design services since 1999. Based out of Los Angeles, the company has a proven record of superior design and development in Southern California and beyond. The full services available include e-commerce, online marketing, Flash multimedia and print graphics.

Frog on Top began in Los Angeles, and has since expanded to include offices in Toronto and Edmonton. They specialize in high end design, Flash, full custom content management systems (CMS), 3D rendering, and blog integration. Their portfolio includes work for automotive insurance, video games, charity drives, and short film channels.
